    Description
    AddBookingWindow
    Represents a window for adding a new booking to the flight booking system.
    AddCustomerWindow
    Represents a window for adding a new customer to the flight booking system.
    AddFlightWindow
    Represents a window for adding a new flight to the flight booking system.
    CancelBookingWindow
    The CancelBookingWindow class represents a graphical user interface window for canceling a booking in the Flight Booking System application.
    DeleteCustomerWindow
    The DeleteCustomerWindow class represents a graphical user interface window for deleting a customer in the Flight Booking System application.
    DeleteFlightWindow
    The DeleteFlightWindow class represents a graphical user interface window for deleting a flight in the Flight Booking System application.
    DisplayBookingsWindow
    A JPanel for displaying bookings in a table format.
    DisplayCustomersWindow
    The DisplayCustomersWindow class represents a JPanel for displaying customers in a table format.
    DisplayFlightsWindow
    The DisplayFlightsWindow class represents a JPanel for displaying flights in a table format.
    LoadingWindow
    The LoadingWindow class represents a graphical user interface window for loading the Flight Booking System.
    LoginWindow
    The LoginWindow class represents a graphical user interface window for logging into the Flight Booking System.
    MainWindow
    The MainWindow class represents the main graphical user interface window for the Flight Booking System.
    PassengerList
    The PassengerList class provides a method to display the list of passengers for a specified flight in the Flight Booking System application.
    PassengerListWindow
    A JFrame for displaying the list of passengers for a flight.
    UpdateBookingWindow
    The UpdateBookingWindow class represents a window for updating an existing booking in the flight booking system.
